source.name: MTB 2012
source.description: TCS compiled the tariff relief database so taxpayers can research what their lawmaker is requesting. It includes the lawmaker, the product that is subject to the tariff, the benefiting company, the lobbyist behind it (if applicable) and the campaign cash involved (again, if applicable).
